title: Terminator Genisys
description: When John Connor (Jason Clarke), leader of the human resistance, sends Sgt. Kyle Reese (Jai Courtney) back to 1984 to protect Sarah Connor (Emilia Clarke) and safeguard the future, an unexpected turn of events creates a fractured time-line. Now, Sgt. Reese finds himself in a new and unfamiliar version of the past, where he is faced with unlikely allies, including the Guardian (Arnold Schwarzenegger), dangerous new enemies, and an unexpected new mission: To reset the future...
castList: [Arnold Schwarzenegger, Jason Clarke, Emilia Clarke, Jai Courtney, J.K. Simmons, Dayo Okeniyi, Matt Smith, Courtney B. Vance, Byung-hun Lee, Michael Gladis, Sandrine Holt, Wayne Bastrup, Gregory Alan Williams, Otto Sanchez, Matty Ferraro]
characterList: [Guardian, John Connor, Sarah Connor, Kyle Reese, O'Brien, Danny Dyson, Alex (as Matthew Smith), Miles Dyson, Cop / T-1000, Lt. Matias, Detective Cheung, Young O'Brien, Detective Harding (as Greg Alan Williams), Detective Timmons, Agent Janssen]
